OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FBy Haleema Saheed, ITV News Assistant
OL,8,FProducer
OL,10,FFor Diaba Konate, a basketball player
OL,11,Fwho excelled for the French national
OL,12,Fyouth team growing up, the prospect of
OL,13,Fa home Olympics should have been a
OL,14,Fmoment of ultimate sporting pride.
OL,16,FYet as the Olympic opening ceremony
OL,17,Fsignalled the start of the games in
OL,18,FParis, Konate finds herself on the
OL,19,Fsidelines, not due to injury, but due
OL,20,Fto a French law that prevents her from
OL,21,Fcompeting with her headscarf.
