OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FAs France prepares to host the 2024
OL,8,FOlympics, an event centred around
OL,9,Fcelebrating athletes from all
OL,10,Fbackgrounds, cultures and faiths - the
OL,11,Fhost nation has found itself heavily
OL,12,Fcriticised for refusing to lift its
OL,13,FHijab (Headscarf) ban.
OL,15,FAnnounced in 2021, France's 'Islamist
OL,16,Fseparatism' has been deemed hugely
OL,17,Fcontroversial, impacting many areas of
OL,18,FFrench society, including competitive
OL,19,Fsports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
