OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FThe rule effectively excludes anyone
OL,8,Fwearing a sports hijab from
OL,9,Fparticipating in competitive sports, a
OL,10,Fban that doesn't just affect on-field
OL,11,Fplayers, but also coaches and referees.
