OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FLast September, with the upcoming
OL,8,FOlympics renewing conversation around
OL,9,Fthe ban, the French sports minster,
OL,10,FAmelie Oudea-Castera, announced that
OL,11,FFrench athletes will not be allowed to
OL,12,Fcompete while wearing a Hijab, and
OL,13,Frefused to overturn the ban despite
OL,14,Fpleas from international human right
OL,15,Fgroups to the International Olympics
OL,16,FCommittee (IOC).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
