OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FThe report highlighted how banning the
OL,8,Fhijab is particularly jarring
OL,9,Fconsidering the 2024 Olympics has been
OL,10,Flabelled as the first gender equal
OL,11,FOlympics - yet Muslim women are being
OL,12,Fdiscriminated against and singled out.
OL,14,FFor Konate, who had been forced to
OL,15,Fmove to the United States to continue
OL,16,Fher playing career, the disappointment
OL,17,Fwas evident.
