OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FShe said: "It's very frustrating to be
OL,8,Fexcluded from representing my country
OL,9,For just being able to play basketball
OL,10,Fsimply because of my religious
OL,11,Fidentity as a Muslim woman who chooses
OL,12,Fto wear hijab.
OL,14,F"I can't fully express my faith and
OL,15,Fpursue my athletic aspiration."
OL,17,FThe IOC noted that French athletes
OL,18,Fwere treated as civil servants and had
OL,19,Fto "respect" French law.
