OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FIt said: "This means that they must
OL,8,Frespect the principles of secularism
OL,9,F(laicite) and neutrality, which,
OL,10,Faccording to French law, means
OL,11,Fprohibition from wearing outwardly
OL,12,Freligious symbols, including the
OL,13,Fhijab, veil and headscarf when they
OL,14,Fare acting in their official capacity
OL,15,Fand on official occasions as members
OL,16,Fof the French national team."
OL,18,FHijab-wearing athletes from other
OL,19,Fcountries have spoken out over the ban.
