OL,7,FTina Rahimi, an Australian Muslim
OL,8,FHijab wearing boxer, took to Instagram
OL,9,Fto share her concerns.
OL,11,FShe posted: "Thankfully I'm still able
OL,12,Fto participate in my hijab, which I'm
OL,13,Fso grateful for.
OL,15,F"But it's so unfortunate for the
OL,16,Fathletes in France because it has
OL,17,Fnothing to do with their performance.
OL,18,FIt should not get in the way of you
OL,19,Fbeing an athlete.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
