OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,F"It's so hard for you to be an Olympic
OL,8,Fathlete and to think that you have to
OL,9,Fgive away your faith to participate in
OL,10,Fthese events. I believe everyone
OL,11,Fshould be equal."
OL,13,FShe added: "People grow up wanting to
OL,14,Fgo to the Olympics and it's all that
OL,15,Fthey work towards, and all that they
OL,16,Fwant to achieve. That would be taking
OL,17,Faway someone's dream.
OL,19,F"I stand by all the French girls...
OL,20,FIt's really, really unfortunate."
