OL,3,C'My Hijab is not your business':
OL,4,COlympic athletes denounce French
OL,5,Cheadscarf ban
OL,7,FIbtihaj Muhammad, the first Hijab-
OL,8,Fwearing athlete to represent team USA
OL,9,Fin the 2016 Rio Olympics, posted a
OL,10,Fpicture on Instagram, holding up a
OL,11,Fsign with the words 'My Hijab is not
OL,12,Fyour business'.
OL,14,FWhen asked about this by Pop Sugar,
OL,15,Fshe described it as a "gross violation
OL,16,Fof our human rights as women, as
OL,17,FMuslims, our religious freedom".
OL,19,FShe hopes people will stand up and
OL,20,Fsupport Muslim women at this time, on
OL,21,Fthe fight for equality.
