OL,7,FAnna Blus, Amnesty International's
OL,8,FWomen's Rights Researcher in Europe,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Banning French athletes from
OL,10,Fcompeting with sports hijabs at the
OL,11,FOlympic and Paralympic Games makes a
OL,12,Fmockery of claims that Paris 2024 is
OL,13,Fthe first Gender Equal Olympics and
OL,14,Flays bare the racist gender
OL,15,Fdiscrimination that underpins access
OL,16,Fto sport in France.
